## Slack Bot Token Verification

To verify your Slack bot token, run:

```sh
curl -sS -H "Authorization: Bearer xoxb-REDACTED" https://slack.com/api/auth.test
```

**Expected output:**
- Should include: `{"ok":true, ...}`

**Troubleshooting if not `ok:true`:**
- **Invalid auth:** Ensure you used a bot token (`xoxb-â€¦`) with the correct scopes.
- **Expired/rotated:** Pull the latest token from `vault://linkboutique/slack`.
- **Network issues:** Retry or test from a different network.
- **App not installed to workspace:** Reinstall via [Slack App Management](https://app.slack.com/client/T04SUHGA5AT) and retry.